Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堵在路上了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Stuck in traffic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科幻有了你出行问题的解决方案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science fiction has the answer for your transportation problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要从地点A发送到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Simply beam from point A 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点B\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to point B.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《星际迷航》里的输送器是那些东西之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The "Star Trek" transporter is one of those things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁都可以进行大量飞行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that any of us who do a lot of flying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿快点发明出来吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}really wish would just please be invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当你着手考虑所需的技术时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But then when you start thinking about the technologies required,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就有点令人生畏了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it becomes a bit daunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在《星际迷航》里 如我们在演出中所描述的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On "Star Trek," as we've depicted it on the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输送器的工作是将人拆成一颗颗原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the transporter works by taking a person apart atom by atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那些原子转换成能量束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}converting those atoms into a stream of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那能量发送到目的地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beaming that energy to the target location,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在目的地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then reassembling all of those atoms 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的原子重组成人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that make up the person at the target location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它们扫描人体的过程中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As they're scanning the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会记录下状态 所有的原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're recording the positions of all the atoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有围绕原子的电子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of all the electrons orbiting the atoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有电子的自旋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the spins of all of the electrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内分子结构的波函数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the wave functions of all of the molecular structures in the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有东西的振荡 运动 速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how everything's vibrating, moving, the velocities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据量非常庞大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The amount of data is enormous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而它们设法仔细地全部扫描\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and somehow they're scanning all of it remotely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后它们设法将人体拆解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then they're somehow taking and tearing that body apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人转成纯粹的能所需的能量将远超过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The amount of energy required to turn a human into pure energy would be 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类迄今制造的最强大的核武器里的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}far more than in the most powerful nuclear weapons that humans have ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其过程本身将是毁灭性的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The process itself would be destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将我这般大小的人整个转换为能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To convert someone my size entirely to energy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将相当于地球上引爆过的最大的核弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be the equivalent 41 times the energy release
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所释放能量的41倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the largest nuclear weapon ever exploded on planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 如果你现在就想传送我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, if you tried to transport me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就得扪心自问一下 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you have to ask yourself 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而传送器传送另一头出来的是什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what comes out the other side of a transporter beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is it you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你的完美量子复制品呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or a perfect quantum replica of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是将人分解并重组呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are they disassembling the person and reassembling them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把人分解后 储存信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or are they disassembling the person, storing the information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在从头重新创造人呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and recreating the person from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个有趣的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an interesting question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送器究竟是把你杀死 然后造出一个克隆人呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Does the transporter actually kill you and then create a clone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是它设法维持你 将你传送到别的地方呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or does it somehow preserve you and transport you to another place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你说 你被分解成一颗颗原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're going to say that you're disassembled atom by atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被转换成了能量束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}converted into an energy stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再别的地方进行重组\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then reassembled someplace else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出 它相比杀死你然后再复活你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't see how that's anything other than killing you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and resurrecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是来源于科幻的装置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It may be a device rooted in science fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是传送技术在现实世界里的前景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the real-world prospects for transporter technology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已引起了美国军方的注意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}attracted the attention of the U.S. military.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空军展开了一项研究\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Air Force commissioned a study
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究未来的物质传送系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to investigate the future of matter transmission systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足为奇 遇上了一些障碍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, not surprisingly, found a number of roadblocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开发有效的传送器是个难题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Developing a working transporter is a tough nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的问题之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among the biggest,
