Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再考虑兆字节或千兆字节了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Forget megabytes or gigabytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅扫描一个人所创建的信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The information created by a scan of just one person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会产生数十亿兆兆字节\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would generate billions of terabytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人用TB硬盘来储存\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One person would take roughly enough terabyte drives' worth of storage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以填满5亿个帝国大厦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to fill 500 million Empire State Buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把个人储存为数据的含义就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the implication of storing a person as data is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否必须立刻传送它们？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}do you have to teleport them immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你把它们非物质化 储存为信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What if you dematerialize them, store the information,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保存50年 100年 5000年又当如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and save it for 50 years, 100 years, 5,000 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个人的角度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From the point of view of that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变成了时间旅行了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it becomes time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬盘的容量在目前的水平上继续改善的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If hard drive capacities continue to improve at their present rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理储存需求的驱动能力就有可能存续\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a drive capable of handling the storage requirements may exist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约200到300年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in about 200 to 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打造物质传送器的最后一个障碍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A final barrier to creating a matter transporter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是量子物理学的一个基本属性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a fundamental property of quantum physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做海森堡的测不准原理\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}known as Heisenberg's Uncertainty Principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最早的《星际迷航》首映之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After the original "Star Trek" premiered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多物理学家纷纷质疑传送技术\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a lot of physicists questioned the transporter technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们谈论的最大的问题之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and one of the biggest problems with it that they talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是确实不可能完全精确地同时掌握\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was that it's really not possible to know with complete precision
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子或亚原子粒子的位置和动量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}both the location and the momentum of an atom or a subatomic particle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 你对物体的位置掌握越多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In other words, the more you know where something is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你对其速度的掌握就越少 反之亦然\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the less you know how fast it's going and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拍一张旋转木马的照片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Take a picture of the merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你无疑能看到旋转木马\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you can certainly see where that merry-go-round is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对附近其它东西的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with respect to anything else that's nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但问题是旋转木马的旋转就有点模糊了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the things that are spinning on the merry-go-round are kind of blurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想重组零零碎碎的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're trying to reassemble the bits and pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来构建已经非物质化了的柯克船长量子形象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that make up a quantum image of a just-dematerialized Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最不愿意看到的事情就是海森堡的量子不确定性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the last thing you want is Heisenberg's quantum uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在《星际旅行 下一代》里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In "Star Trek: The Next Generation,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的技术顾问之一 迈克 奥库达\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of our technical advisors, Mike Okuda,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出了这个叫做海森堡补偿器的主意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}came up with the idea of this thing called a Heisenberg compensator,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是传送器的组件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is the component in the transporter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便地处理那个小问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that conveniently deals with that little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为那是个很聪明的解决方案 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I always thought that was a very clever solution to--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对建造传送器的最大的障碍之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to one of the biggest obstacles in building a transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送器有时会发生故障\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The transporter would, on occasion, break down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在人的传送中一般是很不好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that was generally not good for the person being transported.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有数据在传送过程中丢失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If some data were lost during transport,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最后就会缺眼少脑什么的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you ended up without eyes or a brain or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那显然是个灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that would obviously be disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会丢失一些DNA\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You might lose a bit from your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你的身体具有DNA修复机能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and while your body has DNA repair mechanisms,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无数次修复有可能会导致癌症\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that repeated numerous times could lead to cancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会导致畸形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It could lead to deformities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会导致各种毛病\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It could lead to all sorts of maladies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你真的可能不愿意涉及的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you really probably wouldn't want to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大规模超级计算机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Massively huge supercomputers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海森堡补偿器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Heisenberg compensators,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子扫描 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}quantum scanning--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科幻的方方面面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all part of science fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们如何才能使其成为科学事实呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So how do we make it science fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过来一点幽灵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By getting a little spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因斯坦著名的将其称为 超距幽灵作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Einstein famously called it "spooky action at a distance."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怪异的量子纠缠世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the bizarre world of quantum entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上 两个粒子会以这样的方式互动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Basically, two particles can interact in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它们分开时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that when they become separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个状态会直接影响到另一个的状态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the state of one directly affects the state of the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这种纠缠属性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And using this property of entanglement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以操控一个地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you can manipulate one location
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来瞬间改变另一个地方的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to change what's going on in the other location instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是出自量子力学的一个最诡异的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is about the single freakiest thing to come out of quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法把信息从一个粒子传给另一个粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no way for the information to travel from the one particle to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以将它们分开到的距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can separate them by so much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如果你进行测量 连光速都不会让信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that even the speed of light doesn't allow the information
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一点到另外一点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to get from one point to the other when you make the measurement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个地球上或许就三个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's probably three people on the entire planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全理解这个概念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that fully understand this concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们其余的人就看着运算\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the rest of us just look at the mathematics
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身不舒服\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and get queasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划中的纠缠幽灵作用的测试安排\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Plans are in the works to test the spooky action of entanglement
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通过地面与低地球轨道间的传送信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by transmitting information between the ground and low Earth orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类史上的首次发送\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the first "beaming up" In human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该技术会被利用在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This technology could be put to use in 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一代的超级计算机的研发之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the development of a new generation of supercomputers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算机可能会有朝一日快到足以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}computers that may one day be fast enough
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行复杂计算以满足更加尖端的传送器的需求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to carry out the complex calculations needed for a more sophisticated transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会立马使用传送器的 前提是我要确保\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would use a transporter in an instant if I were assured
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回到家里与亲人团聚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that I could return home to my loved ones when I so desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那将是个奇妙之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think it would be a fantastic trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在J J 艾布拉姆斯重启的《星际迷航》系列中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In J.J. Abrams' reboot of the "Star Trek" franchise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏人以全新的方式用作了科幻的主角\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the villain used a science fiction staple in a whole new way,
